{"tid":1757491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗深一層，有冇機會可以用熱狗同一招去分化返班藍絲做白票黨?","createTime":"2019-11-26T14:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T16:45:30.000Z","uid":197976,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53f97b52981fc02d8d4a0152787bc9f20c9be776","tid":1757491,"uid":197976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"先利申歡迎熱狗負皮，由2015年就已經睇唔順你班分化l<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我諗至少有一件事你地都唔會反對，<br />\n就係你地用盡所有方法去嘗試改變人投票有用嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家藍絲基本上分開兩派:<br />\n1. 深藍深紅，要用盡所有方法都要打死班曱甴，中共萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 現實派淺藍，暴徒阻我返工同日日搞事搞到心都煩，我只係想要平靜香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟認為今次民主派光復區議會係一個唔錯嘅切入點，<br />\n其實響藍絲心入面<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">投票其實唔係公民責任黎</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地只係見有人政綱話可以止暴制亂會就跟風投票，<br />\n咁如果有人散播<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗主義</span></strong>，<br />\n「我地投極票都阻唔到暴徒架喇，而家選舉無論結果同票站職員(佢地自己吹起個風咋)都係倒向暴徒，不如慳返啲時間心力果日約姨媽姑姐飲茶算，政治都是醜惡」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚至係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">挑起情緒</span></strong><br />\n「頂你個肺而家俾啲黃屍玩殘香港，<br />\n而家連個區議會都lam埋但政府又唔做野dq，<br />\n我仲要同你玩體制?<br />\n議會呢啲全部都係垃圾，<br />\n你一日唔槍殺暴徒我一日唔落街投票，<br />\n我同兄弟組隊攞刀斬暴徒，幫解放軍引路算」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後再<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">引發矛盾</span></strong><br />\n「喂你叫解放軍入城搞到股市跌喎」<br />\n「食屎啦就係你班垃圾偏幫曱甴先搞成咁」<br />\n「根本有啲建制就係表面撐政府背地裏偏幫曱甴，冇盡義務維護一國兩制」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯</span>好野啊，輸咁多議席一句都冇怨政府，梗係啦李慧琼都冇輸到，<span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會</span>就唔重要?麥美娟呢?大難臨頭各自飛?」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諸如此類，唔知會點呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再利申本人愛好和平，絕對唔會分化人咁衰嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654283db08696a41e57635424c62d3a6ee7a613e","tid":1757491,"uid":197976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7b4255171e3eacd022ea9333a165ea06bcf73a","tid":1757491,"uid":197976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39c22523ae1c2bd0f34e192ad94afbd04616c85","tid":1757491,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"幾有計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ad5765134cd26ecfeb21f7e4a0a49c37145380","tid":1757491,"uid":197976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0554ab9a16d779e85498453f5eaf9cdf5e0cbc82","tid":1757491,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"好心你唔好同嗰班熱狗玩啦， 你要班藍絲同熱狗玩分化，因住佢哋郜變埋熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4fd22219c0fe3cfa715d0c11c50d869f3babbd","tid":1757491,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0554ab9a16d779e85498453f5eaf9cdf5e0cbc82","tid":1757491,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"好心你唔好同嗰班熱狗玩啦， 你要班藍絲同熱狗玩分化，因住佢哋郜變埋熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"都、"},{"pid":"58ee7597ce1c005a1c8cc462dcac679a8f51a6a2","tid":1757491,"uid":197976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503ae52a32f0c1a1c808a4071204e8176b213672","tid":1757491,"uid":197976,"like":0,"disl